icationHeading\">Alerts In Effect</h2>\n<button aria-label=\"Dismiss\" class=\"AlertsNotification__DismissButton\" type=\"button\">\nDismiss\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#close\"></use>\n</svg>\n</button>\n<span class=\"hr clearfix\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Body\" id=\"AlertsNotificationBody\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLinkContainer\">\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#add\"></use>\n</svg>\n<a class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLink\" href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/conditions.htm\" id=\"AlertsNotificationMoreLink\" tabindex=\"-1\">\nmore information on current conditions...\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"MainContent\" id=\"main\" role=\"main\">\n\n<div aria-labelledby=\"modal-contact-us-label\" class=\"modal fade\" id=\"modal-contact-us\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h4 class=\"modal-title visually-hidden\" id=\"modal-contact-us-label\">Contact Us</h4>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"adminTools\"></div>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div class=\"container\">\n\n</div>\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"ContentHeader text-content-size\">\n<h1 class=\"page-title\">Ranger-led Field Trips</h1>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Layout\" id=\"cs_control_2\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"CS_Layout_Table\" id=\"cs_idLayout2\" summary=\"\" width=\"100%\"><tr class=\"CS_Layout_TR\"><td class=\"CS_Layout_TD\" id=\"cs_idCell2x1x1\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_6776880\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<h3><span style=\"color:null;\"><span style=\"text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\">Spring 2026 Registration is </span></span><span style=\"color:#c0392b;\"><span style=\"text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);\">CLOSED</span></span></h3>\n<p><strong>If you would like to plan a field trip, we encourage you to use the </strong><a aria-label=\"Link self-guided field trip materials\" href=\"/grca/learn/education/self-guided-field-trips.htm\" id=\"menurjt\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"/grca/learn/education/self-guided-field-trips.htm\"><strong>self-guided field trip materials</strong></a><strong>. We also have resources featuring rangers, including the </strong><a aria-label=\"Link village rim walk video\" href=\"/media/video/view.htm?id=1F975F41-EBA5-5E3D-BBB084C892550715\" id=\"menurjv\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"/media/video/view.htm?id=1f975f41-eba5-5e3d-bbb084c892550715\"><strong>village rim walk video</strong></a><strong> and the </strong><a aria-label=\"Link Exploring Geology at the Grand Canyon National Park video.\" href=\"/media/video/view.htm?id=C81DB998-9A6F-416C-BB11-968D31E4E7B4\" id=\"menurk1\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"/media/video/view.htm?id=c81db998-9a6f-416c-bb11-968d31e4e7b4\"><strong>Exploring Geology at the Grand Canyon National Park video.</strong></a><strong> We have even more videos and resources organized by topic here: </strong><a aria-label=\"Link Student Learning.\" href=\"/grca/learn/education/student-learning.htm\" id=\"menurk3\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"/grca/learn/education/student-learning.htm\"><strong>Student Learning.</strong></a></p>\n<p><strong>If you are visiting on your own, you need to request an academic fee waiver through the process outlined here: </strong><a aria-label=\"Link Educational Fee Waiver - Grand Canyon National Park (U.S. National Park Service)\" href=\"https://www.nps.gov/grca/planyourvisit/educational-fee-waiver.htm\" id=\"menurk5\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"/grca/planyourvisit/educational-fee-waiver.htm\"><strong>Educational Fee Waiver - Grand Canyon National Park (U.S. National Park Service)</strong></a></p>\n<p><strong>Enjoy your visit!</strong></p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_6777755\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_6777755\">\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_6776775\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_6776775\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\n<figure class=\"-right\">\n<picture>\n<source srcset=\"/grca/learn/education/classrooms/images/IMG_1979s_2.jpg?maxwidth=650&amp;autorotate=false&amp;quality=78&amp;format=webp\" type=\"image/webp\"/>\n<img alt=\"a group of young student wearing jackets and hoodies are facing towards a park ranger that is giving a program. In the background, buttes and cliffs within a canyon landscape beneath a cloudy sky.\" src=\"/grca/learn/education/classrooms/images/IMG_1979s_2.jpg?maxwidth=650&amp;autorotate=false\" title=\"School group listening to a park ranger on the North Rim of Grand Canyon.\"/>\n</picture>\n<figcaption>Grand Canyon provides a spectacular backdrop for a field-based learning experience. <p class=\"figcredit\">NPS Photo/Ann Posegate</p></figcaption>\n</figure><!-- floating-image alignment  -->\n<h2>Overview</h2>\n<p>Grand Canyon National Park is a wonderful outdoor setting for place-based learning. The park’s Education Team offers ranger led field trips designed for students in grades 3 to 8. Programs support Arizona Science Standards. <br/>\n<br/>\nDue to limited capacity and reduced staffing, field trip <strong>programs are limited to 50 students or less per day</strong>. Registration is required for all ranger led field trips. Programs are free of charge and take place on the South Rim.  <br/>\n<br/>\nIf you are interested in bringing your students to Grand Canyon National Park for a teacher led trip, please visit our <a href=\"/grca/learn/education/self-guided-field-trips.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=2507889,self-guided-field-trips.htm,14078|\">Self-Guided Field Trip page</a>. Fill out the <a href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/educational-fee-waiver.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=1922835,educational-fee-waiver.htm,11006|\">academic fee-waiver</a> and submit via the email address listed on the form.</p>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_6776752\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_6776752\">\n\n<div class=\"container ListingList ListingResults\" id=\"searchListing-D001317F-0832-F8CF-EBBE35CF41231683\">\n<h2>Field Trip Programs</h2>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"results\">\n<a name=\"results\"></a>\n<div class=\"display-list-view\" id=\"display-list-view\">\n<div class=\"info-micro-filter\" style=\"display:none;\">\n<div class=\"result-count\"></div>\n<div class=\"result-selectors\">\n<div class=\"result-facet-Parks_Item result-facet-select\" data-facetfield=\"Parks_Item\" data-facettitle=\"Location\" style=\"display:none;\">\n<form action=\"#\" class=\"micro-filter facet-parks\">\n<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\n<label for=\"sort-by-select-searchListing-D001317F-0832-F8CF-EBBE35CF41231683\">Narrow By Location:</label>\n</span>\n<select multiple=\"\" name=\"result-narrow-Parks_Item\"></select>\n</form>\n</div>\n<div class=\"result-facet-Organizations_Item result-facet-select\" data-facetfield=\"Organizations_Item\" data-facettitle=\"Office\" style=\"display:none;\">\n<form action=\"#\" class=\"micro-filter facet-organizations\">\n<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\n<label for=\"sort-by-select-searchListing-D001317F-0832-F8CF-EBBE35CF41231683\">Narrow By Office:</label>\n</span>\n<select multiple=\"\" name=\"result-narrow-Organizations_Item\"></select>\n</form>\n</div>\n<div class=\"result-count-select\">\n<form action=\"#\" class=\"sort-by\" id=\"result-count-form\"><p><label for=\"result-count-select-searchListing-D001317F-0832-F8CF-EBBE35CF41231683\">Show</label><select id=\"result-count-select-searchListing-D001317F-0832-F8CF-EBBE35CF41231683\" name=\"result-maxRows\">\n<option value=\"10\">10</option>\n<option value=\"40\">40</option>\n</select></p></form>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><!--display-list-view-->\n<div class=\"FilterTags\" style=\"display:none;\"></div>\n<div class=\"ListingResults-loading\">\nLoading results...\n</div>\n<ul class=\"resultsUL\"></ul>\n</div><!--results-->\n</div><!-- col-sm-12 -->\n</div><!-- row -->\n<div class=\"resultsPaginationArea\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</td></tr>\n</table></div>\n</div><!-- col-sm-12 -->\n</div><!-- row -->\n</div><!-- ColumnMain col-sm-9 -->\n</div><!-- ColumnGrid row -->\n</div><!-- end container -->\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 text-content-size text-content-style\">\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\">Last updated: January 21, 2026</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n <!-- ParkFooter -->\n<!--googleon: index-->\n\n</div><!-- end of <div main> -->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!-- the rest of the scripts are leftovers from before the centennial down and should be pared down where possible -->\n\n<link href=\"/common/commonspot/templates/assets/libs/colorbox/colorbox.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n\n<div class=\"modal fade\" id=\"outdated-browser\" role=\"dialog\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n</div>\n</body>",
